itunes:title: #54 - Fuslie Reveals Her Most Awkward Twitch Fail ft. Valkyrae
description: Content Creator and newest addition to the 100 Thieves content creator roster Fuslie comes on for her first episode of the CouRage and Nadeshot Show with special guest Valkyrae. On this episode, she talks about the origin of her username, her infamous "guitar" story which led to a hilarious encounter with PewDiePie, and more!
